                            <comment id="12707852" author="nitay" created="Sun, 10 May 2009 22:55:24 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This gets fixed by &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-1311&quot; title=&quot;ZooKeeperWrapper: Failed to set watcher on ZNode /hbase/master&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-1311&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-1311&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; as well. They&apos;re both just different places of looping because of not handling session expired.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
